tables.table_schema:
CREATE TABLE biomechanical_properties_materials (
  material_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  material_name VARCHAR(50),
  density FLOAT,
  elastic_modulus FLOAT,
  yield_strength FLOAT,
  ultimate_tensile_strength FLOAT
);

CREATE TABLE prosthetics (
   prosthetic_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
   material_id INT,
   prosthetic_type VARCHAR(255) NOT NULL,
   used_for VARCHAR(255) NOT NULL,
   FOREIGN KEY (material_id) REFERENCES biomechanical_properties(material_id)
);

CREATE TABLE material_tests (
  test_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  material_id INT,
  test_type VARCHAR(255),
  test_result FLOAT,
  test_date DATE,
  FOREIGN KEY (material_id) REFERENCES biomechanical_properties_of_materials(material_id)
);

CREATE TABLE biomechanics_materials (
  material_id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
  material_name STRING NOT NULL,
  density FLOAT NOT NULL,
  elasticity FLOAT NOT NULL,
  tensile_strength FLOAT NOT NULL
);

CREATE TABLE prosthetic_users (
  user_id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
  user_name STRING NOT NULL,
  age INTEGER NOT NULL,
  gender STRING NOT NULL,
  amputation_type STRING
);

CREATE TABLE usage_log (
  log_id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
  user_id UUID NOT NULL,
  part_id UUID NOT NULL,
  usage_date TIMESTAMP NOT NULL,
  duration_hours INTEGER NOT NULL
);

CREATE TABLE biomechanical_properties_orthopedic_implants (
    implant_id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
    material_name TEXT,
    density FLOAT,
    tensile_strength FLOAT,
    bending_modulus FLOAT
);

CREATE TABLE biomechanical_properties_prosthetic_limbs (
    limb_id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
    material_name TEXT,
    flexibility FLOAT,
    durability FLOAT,
    weight FLOAT
);

CREATE TABLE biomechanical_properties_joint_implants (
    joint_id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
    material_name TEXT,
    range_of_motion FLOAT,
    stability FLOAT,
    wear_resistance FLOAT
);

CREATE TABLE biomechanical_properties_material_library (
    material_id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
    material_name TEXT,
    density FLOAT,
    tensile_strength FLOAT,
    bending_modulus FLOAT
);

CREATE TABLE biomechanical_properties_mechanical_testing (
    test_id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
    material_name TEXT,
    test_type TEXT,
    test_result FLOAT,
    test_date DATE
);
